      "text": "Radar odometry code which removes motion distortion and Doppler effects from Navtech radar data."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "keenan-burnett/yeti_radar_odometry",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "This repo contains radar odometry code which removes motion distortion and Doppler effects from Navtech radar data. For our odometry experiments, we use the [Oxford Radar Robotcar Dataset](https://oxford-robotics-institute.github.io/radar-robotcar-dataset/). For our metric local\u2026"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "url-kaist/outlier-robust-radar-odometry",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "ORORA: Outlier-robust radar odometry, which is accepted in ICRA'23"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
